      • deepClone

        public FeatureModel deepClone(boolean complete)
        Deprecated. 
        Clones the feature model. Makes a deep copy from all fields in the model.
        Note that: fm == fm.clone(false) and fm == fm.clone(true) are false in every case.
        Parameters:
        complete - If false the fields annotations, comments, colorschemeTable and layout are set to null for a faster cloning process.
        Returns:
        a deep copy from the feature model
        See Also:
        clone()
